src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 除左數理卷會低過phy人之外...不過人地係以美國本科生做調查對象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n外國philo撚Average IQ係次於math/phy major medic嗰d<br />\n唔低下<br />\n唔記得邊度睇過</blockquote><br />\n外國哲學多神人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但中大哲學 印象中收分都唔低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過都係個句啦 自己廢就唔會怨入完個系要乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係大學幾年咁撚柒多資源 唔識裝備自己既<br />\n最低限度 3/4年時間 要英文有大進步真係好難架咩<br />\n定已經慣左公開試反映人既一生實力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d038ecac4e08431d0fba496db153bd427b5a0403","tid":333063,"uid":30510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"A1入哲學，睪業做A1"},{"pid":"14f7760f4ebd0d975e29bde40a4a0bcaa331931b","tid":333063,"uid":126973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T19:28:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>乜都得（好似係）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢錯唔晒喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有哲學家係主張數學係萬物之源定唔知乜野<br />\n不過都係乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nUg咁intro就算9數<br />\n上到mphil phd大把專攻philosophy of science或者再細分</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又真係吹大左少少 <br />\n一般而言 哲學唔算同數學好有關係 學數學又唔洗識哲學  <br />\n除左你研究某D phil of maths, phil of logic 個 d 先會學數"},{"pid":"0609264e514b65eb3e1a97a2921c882c16013e4a","tid":333063,"uid":92017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T01:53:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquo